snippet.title: ANNO 1800 OPEN BETA TRAILER
snippet.description:
Come and join us for the Anno 1800 Open Beta from 12th-14th April! Preload on April 10th, available on Uplay.

Register to Anno Union and get the latest news : https://www.anno-union.com/en/register/

In Anno 1800 the path you choose will change the world. Are you an innovator or manipulator? A conqueror or liberator? How will the world remember your name? The choice is yours.
Players must fulfill the needs of their citizens by establishing numerous production chains, deal with other AI rulers inhabiting your world, and rise to prosperity by building a profitable network of trade routes.

http://annogame.com/buy-uplay 
http://annogame.com/buy-epic
